Package com.bookmatch

Class AppConfig

java.lang.Object
com.bookmatch.AppConfig
@Configuration @ComponentScan(basePackages="com.bookmatch.webscrapers") public class AppConfig extends Object
AppConfig class is a configuration class responsible for defining Spring beans for the application.
